# Pinned versions for the e2e infrastructure.
#
# OAP and UI use `apache/skywalking-oap-server:latest` / `apache/skywalking-ui:latest`
# from Docker Hub. These are the publicly-published images maintained by the
# Apache SkyWalking team, built from the latest release. Upstream's own
# test/e2e-v2/script/docker-compose/base-compose.yml references skywalking/oap
# which is a private CI-only image — we can't use that downstream.
#
# BanyanDB is commit-pinned and the SHA must match what OAP master currently
# expects. Mirror from apache/skywalking test/e2e-v2/script/env and bump
# whenever the upstream file moves.
SW_BANYANDB_COMMIT=d0f41f9ad139c917c1398c2e62a9f7034214495f
